name: lofi butterfly
description: in the early days of the simulation, the creators experimented with emulating insects before moving on to larger beings. a common goal was to see how accurately one could simulate an insect with the least calculations, so massive swarms could be rendered on screen at once. many of the initial results, such as this butterfly, are laughably far off from reality, but their quaintness still maintains a unique charm. collect to attract hope. inscribed by tenorless circa 2019 // genesis collection
